  <h1 class="t-h1 hero__title t-balance">Fragmentation → Wholeness</h1>
  <p class="t-lead hero__lead t-pretty">A long arc — not a leap. The work is the inclusion, not the achievement.</p>
</section>

<section class="section section--sunk fade-up">
  <div class="container">
